#: ../../speaker.rst:2
msgid "Speaker **V2**"
msgstr "スピーカー **V2**"

#: ../../speaker.rst:6
msgid ""
"The micro:bit **V2** has a built-in speaker located on the rear of the "
"board."
msgstr ""
"micro:bit **V2** には、ボードの背面に内蔵スピーカーがあります。"

msgid ""
".. image:: speaker.png\n"
"   :alt: speaker on rear of micro:bit V2"
msgstr ""
".. image:: speaker.png\n"
"   :alt: micro:bit V2 背面のスピーカー"

#: ../../speaker.rst:14
msgid ""
"By default sound output will be via the edge connector on pin 0 and the "
"built-in speaker **V2**. You can connect wired headphones or a speaker to"
" pin 0 and GND on the edge connector to hear the sounds."
msgstr ""
"デフォルトで、サウンドは端子0のエッジコネクタと **V2** の内蔵スピーカーに出力します。"
"有線ヘッドホンまたはスピーカーをエッジコネクタの端子0と GND に接続して、"
"音を聞けます。"

#: ../../speaker.rst:18
msgid "The speaker can be turned off or on using the functions listed here."
msgstr "ここに記載されている関数を使って、組込みスピーカーを無効化または有効化できます。"

#: ../../speaker.rst:21
msgid "Functions"
msgstr "関数"

#: ../../speaker.rst:25
msgid ""
"Use ``off()`` to turn off the speaker. This does not disable sound output"
" to an edge connector pin."
msgstr ""
"組込みスピーカーを無効にするには ``off()`` を使います。"
"これはエッジコネクタの端子へのサウンド出力を無効化しません。"

#: ../../speaker.rst:30
msgid "Use ``on()`` to turn on the speaker."
msgstr "組込みスピーカーを有効にするには ``on()`` を使います。"

#: ../../speaker.rst:34
msgid "Example"
msgstr "サンプルコード"

#: ../../speaker.rst:36
msgid "An example that runs through some of the functions of the speaker API. ::"
msgstr "スピーカー API のいくつかの関数を実行するサンプルコードです::"

#: ../../speaker.rst:38
msgid ""
"from microbit import *\n"
"\n"
"# Check that the speaker is on\n"
"print(speaker.is_on())\n"
"# Play a sound\n"
"audio.play(Sound.HELLO)\n"
"sleep(2000)\n"
"# Disable the speaker\n"
"speaker.off()\n"
"# Check that the speaker is off\n"
"print(speaker.is_on())\n"
"# Play a sound. This will not be heard on the speaker, but will be heard\n"
"# on Pin 0 if you have headphones or a speaker connected.\n"
"audio.play(Sound.HELLO)"
msgstr ""
"from microbit import *\n"
"\n"
"# 音を鳴らす\n"
"audio.play(Sound.HELLO)\n"
"sleep(2000)\n"
"# 組込みスピーカーを無効化\n"
"speaker.off()\n"
"# 音を鳴らす。組込みスピーカーからは鳴らず、端子0に繋いだヘッドフォンまたは\n"
"# スピーカーから鳴ります。\n"
"audio.play(Sound.HELLO)"

